COPY ~%MOD_FOLDER%/itm/AC#PPBUC.itm~         ~override~    // The Leafrunner +3
  SAY NAME1 ~Buckler~
  SAY NAME2 ~The Leafrunner +3~
  SAY DESC ~This buckler is known as The Leafrunner. It was once used by a druid-protector known as Blasanna Leafrunner, and the item was named after her family name. One day, she had to defent her beloved grove and her family from a group of a gnoll army. The tales say that during the fight, she moved as quickly as a lightning, and she defeated half of the army herself. Rest of the gnolls run away, but she became a local hero.
  
Some suggest that her rapid moves were a result of holding this powerful buckler. Others say that it was nature that had her back, pushing her forward, no matter what. Some also say that those that wield this weapon can protect themselves fith wall of energy.

STATISTICS:

Charge abilities:
– May cast Sanctuary once per day (on self)

Equipped abilities:
– Armor Class: +4
– Grants only half of the Armor Class bonus vs. missiles and piercing attacks
– Doubles movement rate
– Saving Throws vs. Ivocation School: +2

Requires:
 4 Strength

Weight: 2~

COPY ~%MOD_FOLDER%/itm/AC#PPTEA.itm~         ~override~    // Herbal Brew in a Mug
  SAY NAME1 ~Herbal Brew in a Mug~
  SAY NAME2 ~Herbal Brew in a Mug~
  SAY DESC ~This brew is made of chamomile, wild honey, blackberry and lavender. It's supposed to calm people down.
  
STATISTICS: 

Weight: 2~